name: Dresser Mouldings
overview: Dresser manufactures oak flooring, timber mouldings, fine wood carvings, timber columns, handrails, volutes, newel posts and balusters. Established in 1987, there aim has always been to produce the best quality product and concentrate on our relationships with our customers. This has developed from purely supplying components to working with our customers, helping them with designs and ideas. Over the years the company has expanded from a small starting premises through to our main manufacturing facility. The main facility concentrates on the manufacture of architectural timber mouldings and fine wood carvings. There range of products has grown over time to include the manufacture of timber columns, curved mouldings, curved handrails and other components. Our products are manufactured from a variety of materials including softwood, ash and oak. Dresser has a policy of using materials from renewable sources.
